credit.credit-words: All things praise Thee—high and low, Rain and dew and sparkling snow, Crimson sunset, fleecy cloud, Rippling stream, and tempest loud; Summer, winter, all to Thee Glory render—Lord, may we!
All Things Praise Thee, Lord Most High

direction-type.words: All were for Thy glory made,
